Tamil Nadu
Dec 05, 2014
Abduction
Description:
			A Mahila court today sentenced a mason to seven years imprisonment for kidnapping a 16-year-old girl in Thiruvakandanour village in the district in 2009.

He was also slapped with a fine of Rs 3,000 by Mahila court judge Mariyayee.

The prosecution case was that the 33-year-old man, a father of two, had kidnapped the girl in 2009 and taken her to various places, including Mettur.

The mother filed a complaint following which police conducted investigations, located the man and the girl at Mettur on Wednesday last and arrested him.

The girl was restored to her parents, police said.


